record.title: GENERAL LEAVE
record.narrative:
GENERAL LEAVE -- (House of Representatives - September 07, 2007)

[Page: H10308]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to allow 5 legislative days in which Members may revise and extend and place extraneous material relevant to the conference report on H.R. 2669 into the Record.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Kentucky?
